20of%20the%20hottest%20fields%20right%20now%2C%20here%20are%20four%20things%20I'd%20suggest%20doing%2C%20especially%20if%20you're%20struggling.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2243384aa5-536d-441c-b032-de132914afb7%5C%22%3E1.%20Start%20small%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20you're%20just%20starting%20your%20career%2C%20don't%20focus%20on%20landing%20your%20top%20dream%20companies.%20You%20might%20think%20you%20want%20to%20work%20for%20Amazon%2C%20Google%2C%20Facebook%2C%20or%20Microsoft%2C%3Cem%3E%20%3C%2Fem%3Eand%20you%20can%20eventually%20get%20there%2C%20but%20it%20takes%20time%20because%20you're%20competing%20with%20the%20best%20in%20the%20industry.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBe%20open%20to%20exploring%20smaller%20companies%20that%20offer%20opportunities%20to%20grow%2C%20learn%2C%20and%20build%20valuable%20skills.%20Smaller%20or%20midsize%20companies%20will%20allow%20you%20to%20wear%20multiple%20hats.%20You%20can%20also%20find%20a%20fast-growing%20startup%20seeking%20Series%20B%20or%20C%20funding%2C%20which%20means%20the%20company%20has%20the%20revenue%20to%20keep%20someone%20employed%20for%20a%20while.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20fresh%20out%20of%20college%20or%20early%20in%20your%20career%2C%20you%20might%20not%20know%20what%20excites%20you%20or%20what%20role%20fits%20you.%20A%20smaller%20company%20can%20allow%20you%20to%20explore%2C%20helping%20you%20figure%20that%20out.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%223364f1e6-fae5-463b-b5ea-77c714bbbe38%5C%22%3E2.%20Be%20willing%20to%20learn%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EBefore%20working%20your%20way%20up%2C%20learn%20as%20many%20skills%20as%20possible.%20If%20you're%20hired%20as%20a%20web%20designer%2C%20don't%20just%20stick%20to%20web%20design%20tasks%20%E2%80%94%20look%20for%20opportunities%20to%20take%20on%20other%20projects%20that%20will%20help%20you%20gain%20additional%20skills.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20you%20work%20for%20a%20large%20company%2C%20they'll%20want%20to%20see%20a%20wide%20range%20of%20skills.%20If%20a%20company%20sees%20you%20can%20juggle%20several%20different%20things%2C%20they're%20more%20likely%20to%20hire%20you%20over%20the%201%2C000%20other%20people%20competing%20for%20the%20same%20job.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETo%20learn%20skills%20beyond%20your%20role%2C%20help%20your%20peers%2C%20and%20see%20other%20projects%20they%20work%20on.%20If%20you're%20a%20user%20designer%20interested%20in%20becoming%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fi-made-100k-graphic-designer-10-months-of-quitting-job-2019-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Egraphic%20designer%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20those%20are%20different%20skills%2C%20but%20you%20can%20learn%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELet's%20say%20you%20don't%20have%20experience%20with%20Java%20or%20Python.%20If%20you%20know%20one%2C%20you%20can%20learn%20to%20translate%20between%20similar%20languages.%20At%20its%20core%2C%20coding%20involves%20a%20lot%20of%20similarities%20%E2%80%94%20it's%20just%20about%20learning%20the%20little%20tricks.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20you're%20struggling%20to%20find%20a%20job%2C%20think%20about%20how%20you%20can%20use%20your%20skills%20elsewhere%20at%20places%20that%20are%20hiring.%20Consider%20if%20you%20can%20transfer%20your%20skills%20to%20places%20like%20manufacturing%2C%20healthcare%2C%20or%20even%20pharmaceutical%20companies.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2289c4a7c2-89d0-4397-b9a6-fd742b24dccb%5C%22%3E3.%20Network%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EDon't%20just%20apply%20to%20random%20tech%20jobs.%20I%20can%20apply%20to%2050%20jobs%2C%20but%20without%20a%20connection%2C%20it's%20unlikely%20anyone%20will%20call%20me%20because%20no%20one%20will%20see%20my%20r%C3%A9sum%C3%A9.%20Networking%20is%20the%20way%20to%20go.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20way%20you%20can%20build%20your%20network%20is%20to%20pay%20attention%20to%20those%20you%20went%20to%20school%20with.%20If%20you%20maintain%20relationships%20with%20your%20classmates%2C%20you%20can%20see%20where%20they're%20landing%20and%20how%20you%20can%20help%20each%20other.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnother%20way%20