20he%20spends%20much%20of%20his%20time%20doing%20data%20analysis%2C%20writing%20SQL%20scripts%2C%20and%20building%20workflows%20to%20automate%20manual%20accounting%20processes.%20He%20spends%20less%20time%20doing%20repetitive%20tasks%20and%20more%20time%20working%20with%20cross-functional%20teams%20on%20new%20business%20initiatives.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%26quot%3BI%20get%20a%20kick%20out%20of%20working%20on%20products%20like%20Search%2C%20YouTube%2C%20and%20other%20apps%20that%20pepper%20my%20phone%20screen%2C%26quot%3B%20Manalac%20said.%20%26quot%3BMy%20success%20is%20no%20longer%20measured%20by%20billable%20hours%20like%20in%20public%20accounting%20either%20%E2%80%94%20it's%20measured%20by%20the%20impact%20of%20my%20work.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhen%20he%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgoogle-manager-left-bay-area-work-life-balance-advice-2024-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Eneeds%20a%20break%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20some%20of%20Manalac's%20favorite%20on-campus%20options%20include%20hitting%20the%20gym%2C%20popping%20into%20the%20arcade%2C%20booking%20a%20massage%2C%20or%20hitting%20golf%20balls%20in%20the%20simulator.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThen%2C%20there%20are%20the%20extravagant%20work%20parties.%20%26quot%3BMuseums%20are%20rented%20out%20for%20Christmas%2C%20concert%20venues%20for%20Halloween%2C%20and%20I've%20even%20had%20team%20outings%20that%20had%20me%20hopping%20on%20a%20plane%20for%20a%20day%20at%20Universal%20Studios%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Manalac.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAnd%20while%20he%20enjoyed%20domestic%20travel%20as%20an%20auditor%2C%20it's%20been%20overshadowed%20by%20his%20global%20travel%20experiences%20at%20Google%20to%20places%20like%20Singapore%20and%20Switzerland.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%26quot%3BThe%20big%20accounting%20firms%20have%20generous%20PTO%2C%20but%20there%20are%20f