gure%20deals%20to%20PMs%2C%20with%20some%20coveted%20stars%20receiving%20packages%20north%20of%20%2450%20million.%20But%20firms%20often%20must%20take%20it%20on%20faith%20that%20PMs%20claiming%20tens%20or%20hundreds%20of%20millions%20in%20profits%20at%20their%20former%20employers%20are%20being%20forthright.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20dirty%20secret%2C%20according%20to%20conversations%20with%20nearly%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Etwo%20dozen%20portfolio%20managers%2C%20recruiters%2C%20hedge%20fund%20execs%2C%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhedge-fund-business-development-job-citadel-millennium-point72-bds-2024-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ebusiness-development%20professionals%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20is%20that%20many%20of%20them%20aren't.%20When%20it%20comes%20to%20performance%2C%20traders%20regularly%20prevaricate%20and%20exaggerate%3B%20it's%20just%20a%20matter%20of%20degree%20and%20audacity.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWith%20%26quot%3B%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Femployees-quitting-corporate-jobs-explain-f-you-fund-savings-strategy-2024-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EF-you%20money%3C%2Fa%3E%26quot%3B%20hanging%20in%20the%20balance%2C%20there's%20even%20greater%20incentive%20to%20embellish%20%E2%80%94%20and%20more%20on%20the%20line%20for%20investors.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BA%20large%20percentage%20of%20PMs%20fluff%20their%20numbers%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20recruiting%20exec%20at%20one%20large%20fund%20told%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%20data-script%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20data-styles%3D%5C%22default-width%5C%22%20data-embed-type%3D%5C%22custom%5C%22%20data-type%3D%5C%22embed%5C%22%3E%3Ciframe%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fdatawrapper.dwcdn.net%2FIn4TW%2F1%2F%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Headcount%20at%20multimanagers%20vs.%20other%20hedge%20funds%5C%22%20data-external%3D%5C%221%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22456%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20hedge%20funds%20have%20always%20tried%20to%20vet%20candidates%2C%20both%20firms%20and%20employees%20face%20a%20dilemma%3A%20Trader%20P%26amp%3BL%2C%20industry%20shorthand%20for%20%26quot%3Bprofit%20and%20loss%2C%26quot%3B%20can't%20be%20gleaned%20from%20an%20AI%20assistant%20or%20bought%20from%20a%20data%20vendor%20%E2%80%94%20it's%20confidential%2C%20proprietary%20information%20belonging%20to%20a%20competitor.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDishonesty%20on%20this%20opaque%20corner%20of%20Wall%20Street%20isn't%20new%2C%20but%20the%20pace%20of%20hiring%20and%20deal%20size%20is.%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EThis%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhedge-fund-investors-push-back-on-talent-fees-2024-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ewar%20for%20talent%20has%20driven%20up%20costs%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20investors%2C%20who%20have%20started%20to%20push%20back.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHedge%20funds%20have%20responded%20to%20this%20pressure%20in%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fexoduspoint-multistrategy-hedge-funds-lower-fees-adopt-cash-hurdle-2024-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Evarying%20ways%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20including%20some%20that%20are%20bolstering%20efforts%20to%20verify%20performance.%20But%20achieving%20greater%20levels%20of%20certainty%20often%20requires%20a%20willingness%20to%20cross%20ethical%20and%20legal%20boundaries%2C%20as%20well%20as%20some%20skill%20in%20spycraft%20%E2%80%94%20cultivating%20sources%20and%20cajoling%20them%20to%20provide%20sensitive%20information%2C%20sometimes%20via%20clandestine%20meetings%20or%20anonymously%20mailed%20documents.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20industry%20professionals%20BI%20talked%20to%20described%20practices%20and%20firsthand%20experiences%20with%20companies%2C%20most%20declined%20to%20single%20out%20firms%2C%20and%20they%20asked%20to%20remain%20anonymous%20to%20discuss%20a%20legally%20sensitive%20topic%20and%20protect%20business%20relationships.%20Their%20identities%20are%20known%20to%20BI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESome%20believe%20tighter%20vetting%20is%20uncomfortable%20but%20necessary%20to%20protect%20investors'%20capital%2C%20but%20some%20find%20the%20descent%20into%20riskier%20legal%20territory%20troubling.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou're%20just%20putting%20people%20in%20bad%20positions%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20PM%20with%20experience%20at%20multimanager%20funds%20said.%20%26quot%3BIt's%20a%20horrible%20way%20to%20start%20a%20business%20relationship.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Chr%3E%3Cp%3ELast%20summer%2C%20a%20senior%20headhunter%20who%20places%20PMs%20at%20multimanagers%20saw%20a%20change%20emerging%20on%20the%20hiring%20front%20lines.%20Before%20finalizing%20multimillion-dollar%20deals%20to%20hire%20candidates%2C%20funds%20were%20making%20a%20bold%20request%3A%20direct%2C%20proprietary%20evidence%20of%20the%20PM's%20trading%20performance.%20Some%2C%20for%20example%2C%20asked%20PMs%20to%20jump%20on%20FaceTime%20or%20Zoom%20while%20at%20home%20and%20pan%20the%20camera%20over%20to%20their%20computer%20screen%20to%20show%20their%20P%26amp%3BL%20in%20their%20company's%20internal%20system.%20Others%20were%20meeting%20candidates%20at%20coffee%20shops%20or%20going%20to%20their%20homes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20some%20PMs%20obliged%2C%20eager%20for%20a%20hefty%20payday%2C%20others%20were%20spooked.%20Violating%20their%20nondisclosure%20agreements%20made%20them%20deeply%20uneasy%2C%20and%20the%20courtship%20stalled.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAny%20PM%20showcasing%20P%26amp%3BL%20is%20violating%20the%20contract%20they%20signed%20at%20their%20current%20employer%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20headhunter%20said.%20%26quot%3BBut%20the%20only%20way%20to%20go%20and%20get%20another%20seat%20is%20showcasing%20or%20conveying%20what%20you've%20done%20at%20your%20firm.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20a%20big%20conundrum%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnother%20senior%20headhunter%20said%20he%20also%20observed%20a%20change%20starting%20around%20the%20summer%2C%20with%20multiple%20funds%20asking%20candidates%20to%20bring%20their%20laptop%20to%20a%20caf%C3%A9%2C%20log%20onto%20their%20internal%20system%2C%20and%20show%20their%20P%26amp%3BL%20to%20finalize%20a%20hire.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20verification%20step%20typically%20happens%20toward%20the%20end%20of%20a%20monthslong%20courtship%2C%20and%20several%20headhunters%20BI%20talked%20to%20said%20they'd%20had%20deals%20fall%20apart%20in%20the%20past%20year%20because%20the%20information%20a%20fund%20requested%20made%20the%20candidate%20too%20uncomfortable.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20happening%20more%20and%20more%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20second%20headhunter%20said.%20%26quot%3BSome%20guys%20balk%20at%20it%2C%20and%20that's%20where%20the%20deal%20falls%20apart.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHard%20data%20on%20the%20extent%20of%20such%20practices%2C%20much%20like%20trader%20performance%20figures%2C%20isn't%20available.%20There%20are%20more%20than%2050%20multimanager%20funds%2C%20some%20with%20less%20than%20%242%20billion%20in%20assets%20and%20others%20with%20more%20than%20%2460%20billion%2C%20and%20management%20styles%20and%20hiring%20practices%20vary%20widely.%20But%20the%20industry%20professionals%20BI%20talked%20to%20said%20that%20generally%20firms%20were%20intensifying%20their%20vetting%20rigor%20and%20that%20requests%20for%20sensitive%20and%20legally%20protected%20information%20were%20becoming%20more%20common.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%20data-script%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20data-styles%3D%5C%22default-width%5C%22%20data-embed-type%3D%5C%22custom%5C%22%20data-type%3D%5C%22embed%5C%22%3E%3Ciframe%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fdatawrapper.dwcdn.net%2FLIvsV%2F4%2F%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Major%20US%20multimanager%20hedge%20fund%20headcount%20and%20returns%5C%22%20data-external%3D%5C%221%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22541%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cp%3EPerhaps%20the%20most%20popular%20and%20ubiquitous%20way%20of%20corroborating%20a%20trader's%20performance%20is%20by%20obtaining%20the%20candidate's%20pay%20history%20through%20W-2%20tax%20records%20and%20deferred-compensation%20statements.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBecause%20hedge%20fund%20payouts%20are%20formulaic%20%E2%80%94%20most%20multimanagers%20pay%20a%20standard%20percentage%20of%20a%20trader's%20profits%20that's%20typically%20upward%20of%2020%25%20%E2%80%94%20a%20PM's%20compensation%20is%20a%20direct%20indicator%20of%20their%20past%20performance.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20multimanager%20exec%20said%20he%20asked%20for%20W-2s%20and%20screenshots%20of%20P%26amp%3BL%2C%20describing%20these%20requests%20as%20%26quot%3Bthe%20same%20thing%20everyone%20else%20asks%20for.%26quot%3B%20But%20many%20states%2C%20including%20the%20hedge%20fund%20hot%20spots%20New%20York%2C%20California%2C%20and%20Connecticut%2C%20have%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hrdive.com%2Fnews%2Fsalary-history-ban-states-list%2F516662%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ebarred%20employers%20from%20asking%20about%20salary%20history%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20PM%20with%20experience%20at%20multimanager%20funds%20said%20hedge%20fund%20business-development%20reps%20had%20been%20pushing%20for%20PMs%20to%20share%20screenshots%20of%20not%20just%20annual%20returns%20but%20monthly%20figures.%20Another%20PM%20said%20his%20current%20firm%20asked%20for%20such%20granular%20detail%20in%20its%20vetting%2C%20including%20subsector%20exposure%20levels%20and%20returns%2C%20that%20he%20had%20to%20compile%20the%20stats%20on%20his%20own%20because%20his%20firm%20didn't%20track%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20third%20told%20BI%20he'd%20shown%20recruiters%20P%26amp%3BL%20from%20his%20firm's%20internal%20systems%20during%20in-person%20meetings.%20He%20said%20due%20diligence%20ramped%20up%20as%20the%20guaranteed%20pay%20packages%20got%20larger.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BTo%20show%20something%20in%20person%20is%20always%20better%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EStill%2C%20other%20hedge%20fund%20professionals%20said%20that%20they%20hadn't%20experienced%20such%20requests%20and%20that%20they%20strongly%20objected%20to%20the%20practice.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20violates%20all%20the%20confidentiality%20agreements%2C%26quot%3B%20another%20PM%20who's%20worked%20at%20multiple%20funds%20said.%20%26quot%3BI%20don't%20think%20reputable%20firms%20would%20ask%20you%20to%20do%20that.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Chr%3E%3Cp%3EHedge%20fund%20portfolio%20managers%20are%20more%20like%20the%20cocker%20spaniel%2C%20a%20gundog%20once%20known%20as%20much%20for%20its%20hunting%20prowess%20as%20for%20its%20loyalty%2C%20than%20that%20Salomon%20Brothers%20trader%20knew.%20Expensive%2C%20tireless%2C%20and%20well%20trained%2C%20they're%20experts%20at%20sniffing%20out%20treasure%20that%20others%20can't%20see%20%E2%80%94%20a%20skill%20applicable%20to%20trading%20but%20also%20to%20other%20vocations%2C%20including%20job%20hunting.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20the%20market%20for%20hedge%20fund%20PMs'%20talents%20exploded%20and%20sign-on%20packages%20stretched%20into%20the%20tens%20of%20millions%20of%20dollars%2C%20scrutiny%20didn't%20always%20keep%20pace.%20And%20some%20PMs%20smelled%20an%20opportunity.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20can%20be%20gamed%2C%20and%20it's%20definitely%20been%20gamed%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20PM%20who%20has%20worked%20at%20large%20multimanager%20funds%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225010%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Upwards%20shot%20of%20a%20man%20in%20a%20trench%20walking%20in%20NYC's%20financial%20district%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F679924d4eb4be2fff9a2859e%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223340%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EJeff%20Hutchens%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20ex-BD%20source%20at%20a%20large%20fund%20recalled%20a%20candidate%20who%20filed%20paperwork%20on%20official%20letterhead%20that%20was%20later%20revealed%20to%20be%20fraudulent%20%E2%80%94%20the%20candidate%20had%20combined%20separate%20documents%20and%20altered%20information.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BGuys%20lie%20all%20the%20time.%20All%20the%20time%2C%26quot%3B%20another%20headhunter%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20the%20funds%20had%20%26quot%3Ball%20been%20burned%20100%20times.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20top%20performers%20are%20typically%20worth%20the%20cost%2C%20and%20the%20top%20platforms%20have%20generally%20shown%20that%20they%20know%20which%20to%20bet%20on%2C%20said%20John%20Delano%2C%20the%20head%20of%20research%20and%20analytics%20for%20the%20asset%20manager%20Commonfund's%20outsourced-CIO%20team.%20That%20doesn't%20eliminate%20the%20sticker%20shock%20for%20investors%2C%20though.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou%20kind%20of%20wince%20a%20little%20bit%20when%20you%20see%20the%20big%20free-agent%20numbers%26quot%3B%20for%20PM%20hires%2C%20Delano%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhether%20it's%20a%20great%20hire%20or%20a%20bust%2C%20investors%20are%20increasingly%20picking%20up%20the%20tab%20because%20of%20the%20proliferation%20of%20pass-through%20fees%2C%20in%20which%20allocators%20cover%20a%20fund's%20operating%20costs%20%E2%80%94%20including%20ballooning%20PM%20compensation.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20September%20report%20from%20Goldman%20Sachs%20said%20more%20than%2080%25%20of%20the%2053%20multimanager%20hedge%20funds%20tracked%20by%20its%20prime-services%20team%20had%20pass-through%20fees%2C%20up%20from%2063%25%20in%202022.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESome%20allocators%20have%20started%20pushing%20back%20on%20expenses.%20They've%20become%20%26quot%3Bmore%20hawkish%20on%20making%20sure%20higher%20fees%20are%20justified%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Jon%20Caplis%2C%20the%20founder%20of%20the%20hedge%20fund%20research%20firm%20PivotalPath.%20%26quot%3BAnd%20they%20are%20trying%20to%20get%20as%20much%20transparency%20as%20possible.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Teacher%20Retirement%20System%20of%20Texas%2C%20one%20of%20the%20country's%20largest%20pension%20funds%20and%20hedge%20fund%20investors%2C%20published%20an%20open%20letter%20in%20May%20arguing%20for%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.pionline.com%2Fhedge-funds%2Ftexas-teachers-pushes-hedge-funds-use-cash-hurdles%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehedge%20funds%20to%20implement%20performance%20hurdles%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20ensure%20they're%20beating%20the%20cash%20rate.%20Dozens%20of%20investors%20signed%20the%20letter.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BKeeping%20a%20close%20eye%20on%20external-manager%20costs%20and%20hiring%20practices%20is%20not%20new%2C%26quot%3B%20Lulu%20Llano%2C%20a%20director%20at%20Texas%20Teachers%20focused%20on%20hedge%20fund%20investments%2C%20told%20BI.%20%26quot%3BIt%20does%20appear%20to%20be%20getting%20more%20scrutiny%20given%20the%20recent%20capital%20flows%20into%20the%20space.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELlano%20said%20the%20pension%20giant%20had%20observed%20some%20multimanagers%20taking%20new%20measures%20to%20protect%20their%20businesses%20amid%20the%20hiring%20frenzy%2C%20including%20lengthening%20sit-out%20periods%20for%20departing%20PMs%20and%20in%20some%20cases%20clawing%20back%20compensation.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOther%20funds%20are%20opting%20to%20take%20a%20harder%20line%20before%20a%20PM%20ever%20enters%20the%20front%20door.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Chr%3E%3Cp%3EWith%20the%20talent%20war%20showing%20no%20signs%20of%20a%20d%C3%A9tente%2C%20hedge%20funds%20face%20a%20tricky%20task%3A%20boost%20investor%20capital%2C%20but%20also%20safeguard%20it%20%E2%80%94%20knowing%20that%20PMs%20exaggerate%20their%20exploits%20%E2%80%94%20but%20don't%20breach%20confidentiality%20agreements%20and%20alienate%20top%20candidates.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20pressure%20of%20solving%20that%20dilemma%20falls%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhedge-fund-business-development-job-citadel-millennium-point72-bds-2024-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehedge%20fund%20business-development%20teams%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20professionals%20responsible%20for%20recruiting%20and%20vetting%20investment%20talent%20%E2%80%94%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhedge-funds-business-development-executive-hiring-talent-war-citadel-walleye-2024-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Egrowing%20and%20increasingly%20important%3C%2Fa%3E%20niche.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAllocators%20don't%20typically%20get%20in%20the%20weeds%20on%20individual%20PM%20hires%2C%20but%20they%20do%20meet%20with%20the%20BD%20teams%20and%20assess%20a%20fund's%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhedge-fund-allocators-due-diligence-multi-strategy-firms-2024-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eprocedures%20and%20systems%20for%20recruitment%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20retention.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBD%20teams%20have%20a%20limited%20set%20of%20tools%20to%20vet%20a%20candidate.%20One%20common%20method%20is%20investigating%20and%20triangulating%20performance%20claims%20via%20industry%20sources%20%E2%80%94%20bankers%20or%20other%20hedge%20fund%20services%20providers%2C%20for%20instance.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20example%2C%20one%20multimanager%20PM%20recalled%20that%20when%20he%20moved%20to%20a%20large%20fund%20a%20few%20years%20ago%2C%20the%20recruiter%20already%20had%20accurate%20knowledge%20of%20his%20performance.%20He%20wasn't%20asked%20for%20additional%20verification.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20these%20inquiries%20have%20limitations%2C%20including%20the%20breadth%20and%20quality%20of%20a%20BD%20team's%20contacts%20across%20trading%20strategies.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESome%20firms%20delicately%20dance%20around%20the%20law%20to%20obtain%20tax%20records%20with%20salary%20history%20that%20corroborate%20past%20performance.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFunds%20can%20use%20tax%20documents%2C%20but%20only%20if%20a%20candidate%20volunteers%20them%20%E2%80%94%20which%20can%20require%20some%20ingenuity%20that%20%26quot%3Bdoes%20not%20go%20in%20hiring%20manuals%2C%26quot%3B%20an%20ex-BD%20source%20said.%20This%20person%20said%20they%20wouldn't%20explicitly%20ask%20for%20such%20information%2C%20especially%20in%20writing%2C%20but%20gently%20prodded%20candidates%2C%20wondering%20aloud%20whether%20there%20might%20be%20anything%20in%20their%20possession%20that%20could%20back%20up%20their%20claims%20and%20make%20the%20firm%20more%20comfortable%20closing%20the%20deal.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou%20can%20lead%20the%20horse%20to%20water%2C%20but%20you%20can't%20be%20like%2C%20'Give%20me%20your%20W-2%2C'%26quot%3B%20this%20person%20said.%20%26quot%3BPeople%20pick%20it%20up%20pretty%20quick%20and%20say%2C%20'Oh%2C%20I%20can%20show%20you%20my%20tax%20filings.'%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224288%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22w-2%20form%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67992f3b7bb3f854015ad3ae%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222848%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3Edtimiraos%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EAnother%20BD%20rep%20said%20many%20candidates%20would%20bring%20up%20the%20W-2%20on%20their%20own.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOther%20firms%20ignore%20the%20law%20entirely%2C%20directly%20asking%20for%20tax%20documents%20from%20candidates%2C%20according%20to%20PMs%2C%20headhunters%2C%20and%20hedge%20fund%20execs%20said%20other%20firms%20would%20directly%20ask%20for%20tax%20documents%20from%20candidates.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20some%20firms%20want%20additional%20certainty%20via%20actual%20P%26amp%3BL%20figures%2C%20especially%20for%20current-year%20performance%20claims%2C%20which%20can%20translate%20to%20millions%20in%20a%20PM's%20overall%20sign-on%20package.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20ex-BD%20source%20said%20some%20%26quot%3Bdetective%20work%20is%20required%20to%20protect%20investors.%26quot%3B%20This%20person%20recalled%20a%20colleague%20visiting%20the%20home%20of%20a%20candidate%20to%20view%20performance%20evidence.%20This%20person%20has%20also%20received%20documents%20via%20FedEx.%20%26quot%3BIt%20doesn't%20have%20a%20return%20address%2C%20but%20it%20has%20the%20screenshot%20I%20wanted%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20really%20a%20slippery%20slope%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%20%26quot%3BYou%20need%20information%20to%20verify%20it%2C%20but%20there's%20legal%20and%20ethical%20ramifications.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHedge%20funds%20regularly%20go%20to%20war%20over%20talent%20defections%20and%20breaches%20of%20their%20proprietary%20information.%20The%20legal%20risk%20for%20any%20individual%20PM%20may%20be%20small%20but%20isn't%20entirely%20theoretical%2C%20and%20firms%20and%20their%20employees%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.law360.com%2Farticles%2F1414767%2Fcitadel-dragged-into-rival-s-47m-poaching-suit%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehave%20become%20entangled%20in%20litigation%20%3C%2Fa%3Eover%20confidential-information%20breaches%20during%20recruitment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Chr%3E%3Cp%3ECitadel%2C%20the%20%2464%20billion%20multimanager%20fund%20run%20by%20Ken%20Griffin%2C%20has%20vocally%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bloomberg.com%2Fnews%2Farticles%2F2024-11-13%2Fcitadel-warns-recruiters-don-t-pitch-fake-jobs%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eopposed%20recruiting%20practices%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20involve%20sharing%20confidential%20information.%20It%20sent%20out%20an%20email%20last%20fall%20warning%20external%20headhunting%20firms%20not%20to%20spread%20the%20firm's%20proprietary%20information%20or%20to%20share%20competitors'%20info%20with%20Citadel%20employees.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECitadel%20is%20not%20alone%20in%20its%20efforts%20to%20color%20inside%20the%20lines.%20One%20BD%20rep%20at%20another%20large%20multimanager%20fund%20said%20that%20asking%20to%20see%20a%20documented%20P%26amp%3BL%20track%20record%20was%20tantamount%20to%20asking%20for%20IP%20%E2%80%94%20%26quot%3Byou're%20asking%20them%20to%20break%20the%20law.%26quot%3B%20In%20quantitative%20trading%2C%20where%20firms%20are%20especially%20protective%20of%20IP%20and%20trader%20performance%20is%20more%20dependent%20on%20a%20larger%20system%2C%20overt%20attempts%20to%20solicit%20confidential%20P%26amp%3BL%20information%20aren't%20common%2C%20several%20sources%20in%20that%20world%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20the%20headhunters%20who%20noticed%20more%20aggressive%20vetting%20this%20summer%20said%20his%20clients%20were%20mixed%2C%20with%20some%20funds%20nonchalant%20about%20asking%20for%20proprietary%20information%20and%20others%20firmly%20opposed.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhether%20stiffer%20vetting%20processes%20become%20prevalent%20has%20ramifications%20for%20the%20hiring%20market%2C%20and%20firms%20that%20accept%20less%20certainty%20risk%20ceding%20an%20advantage%20to%20their%20competitors.%20To%20some%20extent%2C%20he%20said%2C%20PMs%20expecting%20large%20payouts%20will%20have%20to%20%26quot%3Bget%20comfortable%20with%20proving%20P%26amp%3BLs.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOtherwise%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20%26quot%3Bdeals%20aren't%20getting%20done.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20headhunter%20was%20recently%20bemoaning%20yet%20another%20deal%2C%20months%20in%20the%20making%2C%20that%20looked%20set%20to%20fall%20apart.%20Due%20diligence%20revealed%20the%20candidate%20had%20presented%20their%20track%20record%20in%20a%20misleadingly%20rosy%20light.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20a%20colossal%20waste%20of%20everyone's%20time%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fauthor%2Falex-morrell%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EAlex%20Morrell%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E%20is%20a%20correspondent%20at%20Business%20Insider.%20He%20can%20be%20reached%20via%20email%20at%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22mailto%3Aamorrell%40businessinsider.com%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3Eamorrell%40businessinsider.com%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E%2C%20or%20SMS%2Fthe%20encrypted%20apps%20Signal%20and%20WhatsApp%20at%20(262)%20573-1023.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhedge-funds-push-legal-limits-vet-trader-performance-claims-pnl-2025-1%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%