20working%20to%20bring%20its%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftiktok-tied-instagram-social-shopping-among-gen-z-adults-survey-2024-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eshopping%20product%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20market.%20She%20saw%20firsthand%20how%20TikTok%20has%20dramatically%20changed%20consumer%20behavior%20and%20the%20implications%20it%20could%20have%20for%20the%20future%20of%20e-commerce.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENow%2C%20Hawkins%20has%20joined%20AI%20marketplace%20tech%20company%20Teikametrics%2C%20where%20she%20was%20recently%20hired%20as%20president.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20shopping%20experience%20TikTok%20Shop%20popularized%20will%20have%20a%20lasting%20effect%20on%20e-commerce%2C%20she%20said%20in%20a%20recent%20interview%20with%20Business%20Insider.%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EShort-form%20videos%20like%20those%20on%20TikTok%20give%20shoppers%20details%20about%20items%20that%20photos%20and%20words%20just%20can't.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BPeople%20want%20to%20touch%20and%20feel%2C%20and%20you%20get%20that%20through%20hearing%20people%20talk%20about%20it%20and%20describe%20it%20and%20seeing%20it%20at%20the%20same%20time%2C%20versus%20writing%20about%20it%20and%20looking%20at%20a%20picture%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20makes%20good%20business%20sense%20for%20social%20media%20platforms%20to%20build%20shopping%20marketplaces%20like%20TikTok%20did%20with%20Shop%2C%20as%20they%20allow%20users%20to%20go%20directly%20from%20inspiration%20to%20purchase%20without%20taking%20any%20intermediary%20steps.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou%20have%20that%20community%20environment%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20%26quot%3BYou%20have%20all%20of%20your%20friends%20there%20with%20you%20and%20they're%20telling%20you%20what%20they%20think%20you%20should%20buy.%20You're%20taking%20those%20recommendations%20right%20there%2C%20and%20you're%20closing%20the%20loop%20instead%20of%20having%20to%20send%20them%20to%20go%20someplace%20else.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E