of%20disruptive%20technology%20in%20her%20new%20role%20at%20Teikametrics.%20The%20Boston-based%20startup%20uses%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fchatgpt-openai-ai-dictionary-help-understand-nvidia-2023-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EAI%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20help%20brands%20optimize%20their%20performance%20on%20marketplaces.%20It%20focuses%20primarily%20on%20advertising%20spend%20but%20also%20has%20tools%20for%20optimizing%20pricing%20and%20inventory%20levels.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20president%2C%20Hawkins%20leads%20Teikametrics'%20go-to-market%20strategy.%20Part%20of%20her%20job%20is%20to%20help%20identify%20the%20platforms%20clients%20should%20be%20selling%20on%2C%20and%20what%20they%20need%20to%20do%20to%20succeed%20there.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThriving%20in%20e-commerce%20today%20requires%20constantly%20changing%20things%20like%20product%20copy%2C%20imaging%2C%20and%20videos%2C%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20order%20to%20do%20that%2C%20you%20need%20to%20either%20have%20a%20lot%20of%20people%20working%20on%20it%2C%20or%20you%20need%20to%20be%20using%20AI%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20%26quot%3BUsing%20AI%20really%20enables%20all%20brands%20to%20compete%20at%20the%20same%20level%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20being%20able%20to%20produce%20great%20content.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe%20used%20the%20example%20of%20a%20client%20for%20whom%20Teikametrics'%20AI-based%20tool%20had%20made%20around%2075%2C000%20changes%20related%20to%20keyword%20spending.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20don't%20even%20know%20how%20many%20people%20you%20would%20need%20to%20make%20all%20of%20those%20changes%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20%26quot%3BIt%20just%20speaks%20to%20the%20power%20of%20using%20data%20and%20AI%20to%20help%20drive%20your%20business%20and%20results%20as%20quickly%20as%20possible.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-tiktok-shop-ai-transformed-e-com