their%20past%20projects%20in%20person%20before%20hiring%20a%20contractor.%20He%20said%20failing%20to%20conduct%20proper%20due%20diligence%20could%20cost%20homeowners%20hundreds%20or%20thousands%20of%20dollars.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20world%20has%20become%20very%20litigious%2C%26quot%3B%20Novogratz%20said.%20%26quot%3BAnytime%20someone%20walks%20on%20your%20property%2C%20you're%20at%20risk%2C%20so%20your%20general%20contractor%20needs%20to%20be%20insured.%20As%20a%20homeowner%2C%20you%20should%20also%20be%20included%20in%20their%20policies%20as%20'additional%20insured.'%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E2.%20People%20often%20choose%20furniture%20that's%20too%20large%20or%20too%20small%20for%20a%20room%2C%20which%20can%20throw%20off%20its%20entire%20vibe.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225482%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20living%20room%20designed%20by%20the%20Novogratz%20for%20a%20Greenwich%20Village%20home.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6798080e196626c409853727%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%227401%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ENovogratz's%20interior%20design%20style%20effortlessly%20combines%20whimsy%20with%20sophistication.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Robert%20Novogratz%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ENovogratz%20said%20getting%20the%20scale%20right%20is%20key.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFurniture%20that's%20too%20small%20can%20get%20lost%20in%20a%20room%2C%20while%20pieces%20that%20are%20too%20large%20can%20overwhelm%20the%20space.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20same%20goes%20for%20rugs%2C%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E3.%20Homeowners%20who%20don't%20stick%20to%20their%20renovation%20budgets%20might%20buy%20things%20they%20don't%20truly%20need.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%228097%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20kitchen%20of%20the%20Waverly%20Place%20home%20renovated%20by%20the%20Novogratzs.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F679809ed196626c40985376d%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%