0color%20into%20their%20designs%2C%20adding%20a%20modern%20twist%20to%20classic%20styles.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Robert%20Novogratz%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMy%20wife%20and%20I%20love%20color%20and%20patterns%20in%20homes%2C%20but%20sometimes%20it%20can%20be%20a%20problem%2C%26quot%3B%20Novogratz%20said.%20%26quot%3BYou%20might%20see%20checks%2C%20stripes%2C%20dots%2C%20or%20other%20patterns%20that%20just%20don't%20work%20together.%20It%20can%20be%20too%20much.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20emphasized%20that%20great%20interior%20design%20is%20about%20balance%20and%20making%20sure%20all%20elements%20complement%20each%20other%20in%20a%20cohesive%20and%20harmonious%20way.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BEditing%20is%20key%20in%20design%20%E2%80%94%20more%20isn't%20always%20more%2C%26quot%3B%20Novogratz%20added.%20%26quot%3BI%20love%20many%20things%2C%20but%20sometimes%20less%20is%20better.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20Novogratz%2C%20a%20home%20%26quot%3Bshould%20tell%20a%20story.%26quot%3B%20Mixing%20and%20matching%20elements%2C%20like%20having%20%26quot%3Bfive%20different%20hardwood%20floors%26quot%3B%20or%20mismatched%20decor%20styles%2C%20can%20be%20a%20chaotic%20faux%20pas.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI'm%20one%20of%20those%20people%20that%20believes%20everything%20has%20to%20make%20sense%20%E2%80%94%20the%20dots%20need%20to%20connect%20the%20chapters%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E6.%20Homeowners%20sometimes%20back-burner%20structural%20necessities%20in%20their%20quest%20to%20make%20spaces%20aesthetically%20pleasing.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225504%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20Greenwich%20Village%20home%20that%20is%20bright%20yellow.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6798091c7bb3f854015a94ca%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%228256%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EA%20Greenwich%20Village%20home%20that%20the%20Novogratzs%20renovated.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Robert%20Novogratz