re%20efficiently.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAsked%20if%20the%20Bill%20would%20be%20re-introduced%20in%20Parliament%20in%20the%20upcoming%20Budget%20Session%2C%20Mr%20Pal%20said%20that's%20for%20the%20Speaker%20to%20decide.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Opposition%20MPs%20on%20the%20panel%2C%20however%2C%20have%20alleged%20that%20the%20proposed%20law%20would%20destroy%20Waqf%20boards%20and%20lead%20to%20government%20interference%20in%20its%20functioning.%20Reports%20said%2066%20amendments%20were%20proposed%20--%2023%20by%20BJP%20MPs%20and%2044%20from%20the%20Opposition.%20MPs%20from%20the%20Opposition%20said%20that%20while%20most%20recommendations%20from%20the%20BJP%20MPs%20were%20accepted%2C%20theirs%20were%20turned%20down.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20is%20not%20in%20favour%20of%20Waqf.%20I%20have%20been%20saying%20from%20the%20beginning%20that%20the%20BJP%20has%20brought%20this%20Bill%20against%20Muslims.%20It%20aims%20to%20harm%20Waqf%20boards%20and%20seize%20mosques.%20When%20this%20Bill%20is%20brought%20to%20Parliament%2C%20we%20will%20oppose%20it%20there%20too.%20If%20Hindus%2C%20Sikhs%2C%20and%20Christians%20can%20have%20members%20of%20their%20religion%20on%20their%20boards%2C%20then%20how%20can%20you%20have%20non-Muslim%20members%20on%20a%20Muslim%20Waqf%20Board%3F%26quot%3B%20AIMIM%20leader%20and%20Hyderabad%20MP%20Asaduddin%20Owaisi%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECongress%20MP%20Syed%20Naseer%20Hussain%20said%20the%20amendments%20endorsed%20by%20the%20panel%20were%20%26quot%3Bunconstitutional%26quot%3B%20and%20alleged%20that%20the%20proposed%20law%20is%20aimed%20at%20targeting%20minorities.%20%26quot%3BMany%20objections%20and%20suggestions%20were%20not%20been%20included%20in%20this%20report.%20The%20government%20made%20the%20report%20as%20per%20their%20wish%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDMK%20MP%20A%20Raja%20said%20they%20received%20the%20draft%20report%20running%20into%20650%20pages%20at%2010%20pm%20yesterday.%20%26quot%3BHow%20can%20Members%20of%20Parliament%20be%20expected%20to%20give%20a%20dissent%20note%20overnight%3F%20The%20Chairman%20has%20extended%20the%20time%20till%204%20pm%20today.%20Some%20of%20us%20have%20submitted%20dissent%20notes%2C%20others%20will%20do%20so%20before%204%20pm.%20It%20is%20completely%20undemocratic.%20The%20entire%20process%20has%20become%20a%20mockery%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20the%20DMK%20will%20challenge%20the%20legislation%20in%20court.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETrinamool%20Congress's%20Kalyan%20Banerjee%20said%20the%20committee's%20recommendations%20are%20%26quot%3Bwholly%20perverse%26quot%3B.%20%26quot%3BStatements%20of%20the%20victims%20have%20not%20been%20taken%20into%20consideration.%20What%20we%20said%20during%20the%20deliberations%20has%20not%20been%20taken%20into%20consideration.%20The%20question%20that%20arises%20is%2C%20the%20stakeholders'%20view%20which%20we%20have%20expressed%2C%20why%20it%20did%20not%20appeal%20to%20the%20chairman%3F%20JPC%20proceedings%20have%20turned%20into%20mockery.%20All%20other%20views%20have%20been%20ignored%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShiv%20Sena%20(UBT)%20MP%20Arvind%20Sawant%20said%20the%20proposed%20amendments%20are%20against%20the%20Constitution.%20%26quot%3BUntil%20yesterday%2C%20people%20used%20to%20come%20through%20elections%20in%20Waqf%2C%20but%20now%20you%20are%20removing%20elections.%20People%20will%20be%20nominated%20there%2C%20and%20the%20central%20government%20will%20do%20it.%20Today%2C%20there%20is%20a%20provision%20to%20bring%20non-Muslims%20into%20Waqf%2C%20so%20tomorrow%20they%20might%20do%20the%20same%20in%20our%20temples%20because%20the%20issue%20of%20equality%20will%20come%20up%20in%20the%20Constitution%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Sawant%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMany%20objections%20and%20suggestions%20were%20made%20which%20have%20not%20been%20included%20in%20this%20report.%20The%20government%20has%20made%20the%20report%20as%20per%20them.%20Unconstitutional%20amendments%20have%20been%20brought%20and%20the%20rights%20of%20minorities%20have%20been%20harmed.%20The%20amendments%20have%20been%20brought%20to%20single%20out%20the%20minorities%2C%20especially%20the%20Muslim%20community.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Waqf%20(Amendment)%20Bill%2C%202024%20was%20referred%20to%20the%20House%20panel%20on%20August%208%20after%20Union%20Minority%20Affairs%20Minister%20Kiren%20Rijiju%20introduced%20it%20in%20Lok%20Sabha.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1738140540000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-01%2Frjki9k0g_waqf-panel_625x300_29_January_25.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fwaqf-amendment-bill-joint-parliamentary-committee-mockery-opposition-mps-in-waqf-house-panel-say-their-suggestions-ignored-7585859%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Opposition%20MPs%20on%20the%20House%20panel%20examining%20the%20Waqf%20Amendment%20Bill%20have%20alleged%20that%20BJP%20members%20on%20the%20committee%20ignored%20their%20objections%20and%20that%20the%20recommendations%20made%20in%20the%20report%20are%20not%20in%20the%20spirit%20of%20the%20Constitution%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fwaqf-amendment-bill-joint-parliamentary-committee-mockery-opposition-mps-in-waqf-house-panel-say-their-suggestions-ignored-7585859%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Maruti%20Suzuki%20Q3%20results%3A%20Profit%20up%2013%25%20to%20Rs%203%2C525%20cr%3B%20revenue%20climbs%2016%25%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1738140059000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Fmarkets%2Fnews%2Fmaruti-suzuki-q3-results-profit-rises-13-to-rs-3-525-revenue-climbs-16-125012900660_1.html%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Maruti%20Suzuki's%20standalone%20profit%20rose%2012.6%20per%20cent%20year-on-year%20(Y-o-Y)%20to%20Rs%203.525%20crore%20in%20the%20December%20quarter%20