3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20ruling%20is%20critical%20since%20it%20ensures%20that%20admission%20to%20PG%20medical%20courses%20-%20under%20quotas%20allotted%20to%20various%20states%20-%20can%20only%20be%20on%20merit%2C%20i.e.%2C%20on%20NEET%2C%20or%20National%20Eligibility%20%2F%20Entrance%20Test%2C%20scores.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20bench%20of%20Justice%20Hrishikesh%20Roy%2C%20Justice%20Sudhanshu%20Dhulia%2C%20and%20Justice%20SVN%20Bhatti%20said%20that%20as%20citizens%20and%20residents%20of%20India%20%26quot%3Bwe%20have%20the%20right%20to%20choose%20residence%20anywhere...%20the%20Constitution%20also%20gives%20us%20the%20right%20to%20choose%20admission%20in%20educational%20institutions%20across%20India.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20are%20all%20domiciles%20in%20the%20territory%20of%20India.%20There%20is%20nothing%20like%20a%20provincial%20or%20state%20domicile...%20there%20is%20only%20one%20domicile.%20We%20are%20all%20residents%20of%20India.%20We%20have%20the%20right%20to%20choose%20residence%20anywhere%20in%20India%20and%20to%20carry%20out%20trade%20and%20profession%20anywhere%20in%20the%20country%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20court%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BConstitution%20also%20gives%20us%20the%20right%20to%20choose%20admission%20in%20educational%20institutions%20across%20India.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20court%20acknowledged%20reservations%20may%20be%20contemplated%20%26quot%3Bfor%20those%20who%20reside%20in%20a%20particular%20state%26quot%3B%2C%20but%20only%20in%20undergraduate%20courses.%20%26quot%3B...%20considering%20the%20importance%20of%20specialised%20doctors%2C%20reservation%20in%20higher%20levels%20-%20on%20the%20basis%20of%20residence%20-%20would%20be%20violative%20of%20Article%2014.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20in%20an%20important%20aside%2C%20the%20court%20also%20said%20today's%20judgment%20would%20not%20affect%20domicile-based%20reservations%20already%20granted%2C%20and%20that%20students%20who%20had%20completed%20their%20degrees%20based%20on%20such%20selection%20criteria%20would%20not%20be%20affected%20either.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20case%20dates%20back%20to%202019%2C%20when%20a%20two-judge%20bench%20of%20the%20court%20heard%20appeals%20from%20a%20ruling%20of%20the%20Punjab%20and%20Haryana%20High%20Court%2C%20which%20ruled%20similarly%2C%20i.e.%2C%20domicile-based%20reservations%20for%20PG%20medical%20courses%20are%20unconstitutional.%20However%2C%20the%20court%2C%20recongising%20the%20importance%20of%20the%20situation%2C%20the%20two-judge%20bench%20referred%20the%20matter%20to%20a%20three-judge%20bench.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1738132980000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-01%2Fah2nk1so_supreme-court_625x300_26_January_25.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fsupreme-court-news-domicile-based-reservation-pg-medical-colleges-unconstitutional-supreme-court-junks-domicile-based-medical-quotas-7585037%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Supreme%20Court%20has%20struck%20down%20domicile-based%20reservation%20of%20seats%20for%20postgraduate%20medical%20courses%20-%20within%20the%20State%20quota%20-%20ruling%20it%20violative%20of%20Article%2014%20of%20the%20Constitution.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22KJo%20officially%20launches%20Saif-Amrita's%20son%20Ibrahim%20Ali%20Khan%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1738132365000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-117671900%2Cimgsize-41878.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Fkaran-johar-announces-launch-of-saif-ali-khan-and-amrita-singhs-son-ibrahim-ali-khan-films-are-in-their-blood-genes-and-passion%2Farticleshow%2F117670698.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft