ut%20for%20their%20entire%20community.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThere%20was%20this%20one%20child%20who%20had%20been%20mocked%20by%20his%20friends%20for%20saying%20he%20was%20going%20to%20Switzerland.%20They%20thought%20he%20was%20lying%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20entrepreneur%20adds.%20%E2%80%9CBut%20when%20he%20started%20posting%20pictures%20and%20videos%20on%20Instagram%2C%20his%20friends%20finally%20believed%20him.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20impact%20of%20this%20experience%20was%20evident%20not%20only%20in%20the%20children%E2%80%99s%20achievements%20but%20in%20their%20future%20prospects.%20Two%20of%20the%20five%20students%20from%20the%20team%20went%20on%20to%20receive%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F269061%2Fleena-nair-chanel-ceo-unilever-kolhapur-maharastra-london-inspiring%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eadmissions%20into%20top%20engineering%20colleges%3C%2Fa%3E.%20These%20students%2C%20once%20overlooked%20and%20underestimated%2C%20are%20now%20role%20models%20for%20other%20government%20school%20children.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EShaping%20the%20next%20generation%20of%20problem-solvers%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECurrently%2C%20TIS%20is%20working%20on%20the%20%E2%80%98Nurturing%20Innovators%E2%80%99%20programme%2C%20which%20has%20become%20a%20key%20initiative%20in%20shaping%20the%20next%20generation%20of%20problem-solvers.%20Through%20this%20programme%2C%20private%20school%20students%20are%20encouraged%20to%20identify%20real-world%20challenges%20and%20design%20technological%20solutions%20to%20address%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20notable%20example%20comes%20from%20a%20student%20who%20realised%20that%20government%20hospitals%20are%20often%20understaffed%20and%20it%20is%20difficult%20to%20cater%20to%20every%20bed.%20%E2%80%9CShe%20observed%20that%20when%20an%20IV%20drip%20was%20missing%20from%20any%20bed%2C%20there%20was%20no%20immediate%20way%20for%20the%20hospital%20staff%20to%20be%20alerted%2C%E2%80%9D%20Meenal%20explains.%20%E2%80%9CThis%20inspired%20her%20to%20design%20a%20device%20that%20would%20notify%20the%20central%20monitoring%20unit%20in%20the%20hospital%20room%2C%20whenever%20something%20went%20wrong%20with%20an%20IV%20drip.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20she%20presented%20her%20solution%20to%20the%20dean%20of%20Nair%20Hospital%2C%20he%20was%20so%20impressed%20by%20its%20potential%20that%20he%20expressed%20interest%20in%20customising%20it%20further%20to%20make%20the%20solution%20even%20more%20practical%20and%20effective%20for%20the%20hospital%20staff.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnother%20story%20that%20the%20founder%20shares%20is%20that%20of%20a%20class%2011%20student%2C%20who%20is%20also%20a%20Kathak%20dancer.%20%E2%80%9CRealising%20that%20deaf%20children%20struggle%20to%20connect%20with%20music%2C%20she%20invented%20a%20wristband%20that%20tracks%20sound%20waves%20and%20converts%20them%20into%20vibrations.%20This%20allows%20the%20wearer%20to%20dance%20along%20with%20the%20beats%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20government%20school%20children%2C%20TIS%20has%20launched%20Project%20Udaan%2C%20pathways%20for%20engineering.%20%E2%80%9CIt%20is%20designed%20for%20students%20of%20classes%205%20to%2012.%20The%20programme%20starts%20by%20laying%20a%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F292528%2Fengineer-shoaib-dar-started-pi-jam-foundation-to-provide-free-computer-coding-to-rural-kids%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Estrong%20foundation%20in%20digital%20literacy%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20communication%2C%20and%20mathematical%20skills.%20Then%2C%20we%20gradually%20build%20on%20these%20with%20problem-solving%20techniques%2C%20an%20introduction%20to%20robotics%20through%20hands-on%20learning%2C%20and%20eventually%20a%20course%20on%20web%20app%20development%2C%E2%80%9D%20Meenal%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3ESuccessful%20impact%20and%20future%20growth%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20work%20with%20both%20private%20and%20government%20school%20children%20because%20they%20have%20so%20much%20to%20learn%20from%20each%20other.%20At%20our%20TIS%20centres%20in%20Mumbai%20and%20Bengaluru%2C%20it%E2%80%99s%20truly%20heartwarming%20to%20watch%20them%20interact%20and%20collaborate%20so%20beautifully.%20When%20they%20come%20through%20our%20doors%2C%20they%20leave%20behind%20the%20labels%20of%20their%20outside%20worlds%20and%20assist%20each%20other%20to%20grow%20in%20life%2C%E2%80%9D%20Meenal%20shares.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CBefore%20joining%20TIS%2C%20I%20was%20just%20a%20curious%20kid%20with%20a%20love%20for%20programming%2C%20but%20I%20had%20no%20way%20to%20explore%20it%20fully%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%2019-year-old%20Pritam%20Thopate%2C%20a%20second-year%20computer%20science%20engineering%20student%20at%20Terna%20Engineering%20College.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%201600px)%20100vw%2C%201600px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F01%2FWhatsApp-Image-2025-01-14-at-16.46.22_11zon-1737182779.jpeg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221600%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Meenal%20aims%20to%20guide%20one%20million%20children%20by%202030%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F01%2FWhatsApp-Image-2025-01-14-at-16.46.22_11zon-1737182779.jpeg%201600w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F01%2FWhatsApp-Image-2025-01-14-at-16.46.22_11zon-1737182779-300x225.jpeg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F01%2FWhatsApp-Image-2025-01-14-at-16.46.22_11zon-1737182779-500x375.jpeg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F01%2FWhatsApp-Image-2025-01-14-at-16.46.22_11zon-1737182779-768x576.jpeg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2F